+      and/or OMVS files.
  %I+Info on the repository
  %V+View the OMVS file system for the local repository
+    - Open the ISPF 3.17 (UDList) to allow viewing of the local repository
  %D+Delete the repository on the local file system with prompts for:
     - Removal of OMVS files
+    - Deletion of z/OS datasets
